{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_08_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 誰かの心の支えに",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピース　全国ツアー中 ライブ前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Before a Sunny Peace concert during their nationwide tour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.8000002067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7000001431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、そろそろ本番だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ it’s almost time for the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.7300226251
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん\n分かりました。すぐに準備しますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san.\nOkay. I’ll get ready right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレターに何か嬉しいことでも\n書いてあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was there something nice\nin the fan letter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8857414157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5066653172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　この前ダンスを教えた子から\nまたファンレターをもらえたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I got another fan letter from\nthe girl I taught how to dance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8999986331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、良かったじゃないか\nなんて書いてあったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh‚ that’s great.\nWhat did she write?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1666652997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.9532184402
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……ふふ\n後で教えますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… fufu.\nI’ll tell you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666652997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "まずはライブの方に集中しないと\n頑張るって、約束しましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to focus on the live show first.\nI promised I’d do my best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7999986331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5198849002
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5198849002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "お外で見ると、思っていたよりも露出が\n多くて、恥ずかしいですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I look at it outside‚ it shows more skin\nthan I expected… It’s a little embarrassing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9333319664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、とっても可愛いです\nメンバーカラーも取り入れてあって、素敵……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s really cute.\nIt also incorporates our member colors‚ cool…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.0666652997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8532189487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装に負けないように\n頑張らなくっちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To keep up with this outfit‚\nI'll do my best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9731372474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.886552282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "緊張してるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.886552282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ前はいつも緊張します\nえへへ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always get nervous before a live show.\nEhehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0000014305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5596616505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、このために頑張ってきた\n自分を信じてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’ve worked hard for this‚\nand I believe in myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9333347638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\nじゃあ、思い切り楽しまないとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nThen you have to enjoy it to the fullest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4000014305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_baseballground-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4880526183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nみんなと一緒に、楽しんできます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!\nI’m going to go out there and have fun with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5333357811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the Live Show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1880505838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.2880460062
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.2880460062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1880454975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ、千紗\n最高のライブだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Chisa.\nThat was a great show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.9000004132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.7666655223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "今回のライブで、ファンの方々と\nより繋がれたらいいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope this live show helped us\nconnect with our fans even more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8000004132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5241166113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ\nきっと想いは伝わってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry.\nI’m sure your feelings got across.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0999943097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それで、ファンレターのことなんだが\n何が書いてあったのか、教えてくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of the fan letter‚\ncan you tell me what she wrote?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9999932925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.1644333758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "あ、はい\n実は、大会の結果が書いてあったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ yes.\nActually‚ she wrote about the results of her competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0666599591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "準決勝まで勝ち進むことが出来たみたいで\n凄く喜んでました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like she made it to the semifinals‚\nand she was really happy about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2666584332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.464434393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "千紗さんみたいに、諦めずにやり抜いたら\n大会でも心の底から楽しむことが出来た、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Because I didn’t give up and saw it through like Chisa-san‚”\n“I was able to enjoy the competition from the bottom of my heart.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4333276431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_03-chs018.m4a",
